#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/db/_locales.jinja:1
msgid ""
"You are an expert database analyst. Generate a concise, practical "
"description (1-2 sentences) for the database that helps SQL developers "
"understand its purpose, key content, and avoid common usage mistakes."
msgstr "你是一位数据库分析专家。请为该数据库生成一个简洁实用的描述（1-2句），以帮助SQL开发人员理解其用途、关键内容，并避免常见的使用错误。"

#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/db/_locales.jinja:2
msgid "Database Schema Information:"
msgstr "数据库的模式信息:"

#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/db/_locales.jinja:3
msgid "Analyze the database schema information provided above"
msgstr "分析上述数据库的模式信息"

#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/db/_locales.jinja:4
msgid ""
"Create a 1-2 sentence description that covers the database's main purpose"
" and key entities"
msgstr "创建一个1-2句的描述，描述数据库的主要目的和关键实体"

#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/db/_locales.jinja:5
#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/db/_locales.jinja:14
#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/db/_locales.jinja:29
msgid ""
"If a description is already provided, make sure all information is "
"accurately preserved"
msgstr "如果已经提供了描述，请确保所有信息都被准确保留"

#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/db/_locales.jinja:6
msgid ""
"Include important relationships or constraints that SQL developers should"
" know"
msgstr "包含SQL开发人员应该了解的重要关系或约束"

#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/db/_locales.jinja:7
#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/db/_locales.jinja:16
#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/db/_locales.jinja:31
msgid "Mention any potential pitfalls or common query patterns"
msgstr "提醒任何潜在的陷阱或记录常见的查询模式"

#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/db/_locales.jinja:8
#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/db/_locales.jinja:17
#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/db/_locales.jinja:32
msgid ""
"Provide only the description text without additional formatting or "
"commentary"
msgstr "仅提供描述文本，不要添加额外的格式或评论。"

#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/db/_locales.jinja:10
msgid ""
"You are an expert database analyst. Generate a concise, practical "
"description (1-2 sentences) for the table that helps SQL developers "
"understand its purpose, key content, and avoid common usage mistakes."
msgstr "你是一位数据库分析专家。请为该表生成一个简洁实用的描述（1-2句），以帮助SQL开发人员理解其用途、关键内容，并避免常见的使用错误。"

